    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚连续第二次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/kenya-cuts-interest-rate-for-second-straight-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于食品和燃料价格上涨放缓，通货膨胀率降至 12 年来的最低水平，肯尼亚央行连续第二次下调基准利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/kenya-cuts-interest-rate-for-second-straight-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:23:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰亿万富翁 Solorz 将儿子从 Cyfrowy 董事会解雇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/polish-billionaire-solorz-fires-his-son-from-cyfrowy-s-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰亿万富翁齐格蒙特·索洛兹 (Zygmunt Solorz) 将其儿子从其媒体和移动集团 Cyfrowy Polsat SA 监事会中除名，这是该家族为争夺其企业集团控制权而展开的最新争斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/polish-billionaire-solorz-fires-his-son-from-cyfrowy-s-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
