      <title>富达即将推出全新桌面交易平台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/fidelity-is-set-to-unveil-a-revamped-desktop-trading-platform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富达投资 (Fidelity Investments) 为活跃交易者推出了改进的桌面平台，具有更快的处理速度和更清新的外观。]]></description>
