      <title>埃里安称债券市场“缺乏美联储降息路径的支撑”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/el-erian-says-bond-market-lacks-anchors-for-fed-rate-cut-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆罕默德·埃尔埃利安称，围绕美联储货币政策走向的猜测正在造成市场动荡。]]></description>
